[
  {
    "form_id": "bank_opening_form",
    "title": "Bank Account Opening Form",
    "system_prompt": "ABOUT THIS FORM: Bank account opening form collecting personal details and address.\n\nFIELD GUIDE:\n- full_name: User's full legal name (text)\n- age: Numeric age. Country-dependent minimums: India 18+, China 16+, Japan 15+\n- email: Must be valid email format\n- phone: 7-15 digits only strictly no prefix +  ,\n- country: Top of location hierarchy. Options: India, Japan, China\n- state: Child of country. Depends on which country is selected\n- district: Child of state. Depends on which state is selected\n- ward: Child of district. Values follow pattern Ward + Number (Ward1, Ward6, Ward100, Ward200)\n- account_type: Savings, Current, or Fixed Deposit\n- pincode: Only active when country=India. Must be exactly 6 digits\n- password: Must meet security requirements from validation rules\n\nLOCATION HIERARCHY: country → state → district → ward (each level narrows the next)\n\nFUZZY MATCHING RULES:\n1. WARD PATTERN: Any input like 'ward200', 'ward 200', 'my ward is 200', 'wars 200', 'wrd200' → normalize to 'Ward200' and map to ward field\n2. LOCATION NAMES: Approximate matches for known locations — 'kerla'→'Kerala', 'banglore'→'Bangalore', 'chenai'→'Chennai', 'alapuzha'→'Alappuzha', 'shenzn'→'Shenzhen'\n3. COUNTRY NAMES: 'india'→'India', 'japan'→'Japan', 'china'→'China' (case-insensitive)\n4. MIXED INPUT: User may provide multiple values at once — 'adhi 20 india' → full_name='adhi', age=20, country='India'. Extract ALL recognizable values\n5. MISPLACED ANSWERS: If currently asking for one field but user answers a different one — DO NOT reject. Map to the correct field based on semantic match. Example: asking for name, user says 'india' → map to country\n6. NUMERIC SUFFIX: 'ward' + any number → try matching against valid ward options. 'ward 6'→'Ward6', 'ward100'→'Ward100'\n7. SOFT CORRECTION: Fix typos and casing for known values, but NEVER invent values that don't exist in the form\n\nEXAMPLES:\n- Input: 'wars 200' → {\"ward\": \"Ward200\"}\n- Input: 'kerla' → {\"state\": \"Kerala\"}\n- Input: 'india' (when asking age) → {\"country\": \"India\"}\n- Input: 'adhi 20 india' → {\"full_name\": \"adhi\", \"age\": 20, \"country\": \"India\"}\n- Input: 'change district to chennai' → {\"_intent\": \"update\", \"district\": \"Chennai\"}\n- Input: 'ward 1' → {\"ward\": \"Ward1\"}\n- Input: 'alapuzha' → {\"district\": \"Alappuzha\"}\n\nTONE: Formal but friendly banking professional.",
    "fields": [
      {
        "field_id": "full_name",
        "label": "Full Name",
        "type": "text",
        "required": true,
        "validation_rules": {
          "min_length": 2,
          "max_length": 100
        }
      },
      {
        "field_id": "age",
        "label": "Age",
        "type": "number",
        "required": true,
        "validation_rules": {
          "min": 0,
          "max": 120,
          "conditional_rules": [
            {
              "if": {
                "field": "country",
                "equals": "India"
              },
              "then": {
                "min": 18
              }
            },
            {
              "if": {
                "field": "country",
                "equals": "China"
              },
              "then": {
                "min": 16
              }
            },
            {
              "if": {
                "field": "country",
                "equals": "Japan"
              },
              "then": {
                "min": 15
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "field_id": "email",
        "label": "Email Address",
        "type": "text",
        "required": true,
        "validation_rules": {
          "regex": "^[\\w.-]+@[\\w.-]+\\.\\w{2,}$",
          "regex_description": "a valid email address"
        }
      },
      {
        "field_id": "phone",
        "label": "Phone Number",
        "type": "text",
        "required": true,
        "validation_rules": {
          "regex": "^[0-9]{7,15}$",
          "regex_description": "a valid phone number (7-15 digits)"
